      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just worried because i've been feeling a bit lightheaded today too, so i'm scared if i don't get the full amount in my system it'll be bad. if i take the 40mg now, won't that just make sure the levels are where they need to be for the rest of the day? it feels safer to just get it all over with.",
